<h1>Sharpening</h1>
<p>I can hand sharpen your knives. Everything is done by hand with bench stones, stropps, and polishing tape. Your knife steel allowing, I gaurentee a razor sharp edge. If you can't shave with it, it's not sharp.</p>
<h2>Pricing</h2>
<p>I charge $4 per inch of blade plus shipping costs if you send your knife in to be sharpened.</p>
